49
00:02:19,716 --> 00:02:20,783
I wish everyone would.

50
00:02:20,783 --> 00:02:22,750
I'd hang, but we're headed to court.

51
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:24, 50
I know, that's why I'm here.

52
