00:05:59,816 --> 00:06:01,183
Can you give us a couple comments

121
00:06:01,183 --> 00:06:02,983
about the island, Mr. Queen? Before you go, sir, please.

122
00:06:02,983 --> 00:06:04,983
Couple of comments about the island, sir. What happened in there?

123
00:06:04,983 --> 00:06:09,250
Everybody, step back. Hey man, I'll make you swallow that Nikon. Back!

124
00:06:09,250 --> 00:06:11, 83
(CAR DRIVING AWAY)

