00:06:12,550 --> 00:06:15,750
This happens to you a lot, doesn't it?

126
00:06:16,683 --> 00:06:18,483
How much is a life worth?

127
00:06:18,483 --> 00:06:20,750
A life of a man, a good man,

128
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:24,750
a stevedore on the docks of the city in which we live.

129
00:06:26,483 --> 00:06:27,683
A father.

130
00:06:27,683 --> 00:06:29, 16
(THUDDING) A man with a daughter.

