00:06:36,483 --> 00:06:38,816
was taking bribes from the Chinese Triads

135
00:06:38,816 --> 00:06:40,616
to smuggle drugs into our city.

136
00:06:40,616 --> 00:06:43,483
And when Victor Nocenti   threatened to tell the police,

