00:08:37,208 --> 00:08:39,708
I hired you to protect my son.

167
00:08:39,708 --> 00:08:41,208
Now, I'm not a professional bodyguard,

168
00:08:41,208 --> 00:08:44,342
but it seems to me that the first requirement would be managing to stay

169
00:08:44,342 --> 00:08:45,875
next to the man you're hired to protect.

170
00:08:45,875 --> 00:08:49,175
