189
00:09:40, 75 --> 00:09:43,475
And I am not going through that again.

190
00:09:45,408 --> 00:09:46,975
Okay.

191
00:09:48,775 --> 00:09:50,542
Digg's my guy.

192
00:09:51,942 --> 00:09:53,475
Thank you.

193
00:09:57,942 --> 00:10:00,642
Sorry to give you so much grief.

194
00:10:01,175 --> 00:10:03,108
I served three tours in Afghanistan, Mr. Queen.

195
00:10:03,108 --> 00:10:07, 75
You don't even come close to my definition of grief.

196
00:10:07,642 --> 00:10:09,642
But I tell you what...

197
00:10:10, 75 --> 00:10:11,575
You ditch me one more time,

198
00:10:11,575 --> 00:10:13,942
