00:11:29,675 --> 00:11:30,442
(SCOFFING)

225
00:11:30,442 --> 00:11:31,975
Well, you know, I'd be very much inclined

226
00:11:31,975 --> 00:11:35,642
to believe an honest, upstanding businessman like yourself,

227
00:11:35,642 --> 00:11:39,508
except, well, one of my men

228
00:11:41,442 --> 00:11:42,908
found this at your docks.

229
00:11:42,908 --> 00:11:46,275
You see, there's this vigilante running around.

230
00:11:46,275 --> 00:11:47,742
He thinks he's some kind of Robin Hood.

231
00:11:47,742 --> 00:11:50,242
He's robbing the rich, he's trying to teach them a lesson I guess.

232
00:11:50,242 --> 00:11:53,675
I don't know, I don't know. But the point is,

233
00:11:53,675 --> 00:11:54,908
the man's a killer.

234
00:11:54,908 --> 00:12:00,775
And nothing, and no one, is going to stop me from bringing him down.

235
00:12:00,775 --> 00:12:02,575
But like you said...

236
00:12:06,175 --> 00:12:07,608
Hmm!

237
00:12:09,542 --> 00:12:12,408
...clearly, nothing happened here last night.

238
00:12:12,408 --> 00:12:15,975
Isn't this a conflict of interest, Detective?

239
00:12:15,975 --> 00:12:18,242
